description.narrative: The project has three development objectives: (i) to promote more efficient management and operation of selected public irrigation schemes by participating farmers; (ii) to improve access and consumption of drinking water for rural households in communities un-served or poorly serviced at the beginning of the Project; and (iii) to assist MARH, MEDD and other stakeholders to make better decisions relating to integrated water resources management.
